♪If you can see me♪

2
00:00:07,740 --> 00:00:11,180
♪Holding myself back for you♪

3
00:00:11,220 --> 00:00:14,940
♪The past rides the wind into the horizon♪

4
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:18,380
♪Taking our beginning into oblivion♪

5
00:00:18,460 --> 00:00:21,860
♪In the dim light♪

6
00:00:22,020 --> 00:00:25,540
♪You and I stare at each other♪

7
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:29,140
♪Our fate turns into an illusion♪

8
00:00:29,220 --> 00:00:32,660
♪Who feels more hopeless now?♪

9
00:00:32,860 --> 00:00:37,180
♪So, I will just sit by your side♪

10
00:00:37,220 --> 00:00:42,460
=Passionate Love=

11
00:00:42,460 --> 00:00:45,340
=Episode 16=
(You're The One I Like)

12
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:47,640
In this case,

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:48,670
wonderful.

14
00:00:49,110 --> 00:00:50,320
I'll start preparing for the wedding.

15
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:52,430
Xunchu, do you have time this afternoon?

16
00:00:52,734 --> 00:00:54,430
Why don't you accompany us
to pick the wedding dress?

17
00:00:59,030 --> 00:01:00,920
I'm full. I'll go check the account book.

18
00:01:01,150 --> 00:01:01,920
Enjoy your meal.

19
00:01:06,310 --> 00:01:07,070
She got shy.

20
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,280
Miss Lin, you are really lucky.

21
00:01:23,590 --> 00:01:26,070
These designs are currently popular
in the West.

22
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,350
Mr. Song ordered these.

23
00:01:28,590 --> 00:01:29,400
My bride

24
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,480
will have the most unique wedding dress.

25
00:01:32,350 --> 00:01:33,927
How could I let her
wear the same dress as others?

26
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:37,040
Miss Lin,

27
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,310
why don't you try this on?

28
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,310
Of course.

29
00:01:42,510 --> 00:01:43,280
Put these away.

30
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:50,400
Xunchu, where are you going?

31
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:52,230
Washroom.

32
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,430
Why are you in here?

33
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:29,910
Do you want to marry him?

34
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:31,590
- I...
- Answer me.

35
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,800
Xunrui is your brother.

36
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,470
I am his fiancee.

37
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,520
It's only right that I marry him.

38
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:40,910
Xunchu,

39
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,560
he was almost burned to death

40
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,750
to save us.

41
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,470
We don't know how much he suffered

42
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:46,967
in the hands of Song Zhenyuan
over the years.

43
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,310
Neither of us

44
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,430
should owe him anything again.

45
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:51,800
Do you love him?

46
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,520
Does it even matter?

47
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,000
My father betrothed me

48
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,590
to him when I was a child.

49
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:04,080
This is also my father
and the Commander's final wish.

50
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,630
No matter what it is,

51
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,080
I must marry him

52
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:08,960
now that he is still alive.

53
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,120
Wenyu.

54
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,280
Are you done?

55
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:23,680
Get out.

56
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,470
You haven't answered me.

57
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,360
Do you really want to marry him?

58
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,240
Tell me if you don't.

59
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,030
I'll talk to him.

60
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:33,750
Wenyu.

61
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,240
Have you changed into the dress?

62
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:37,560
Go, get out.

63
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,400
Wenyu.

64
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:44,800
Wenyu, are you alright?

65
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:47,310
- What's going on?
- I'm fine, Xunrui.

66
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:49,520
This dress doesn't seem to fit.

67
00:03:49,710 --> 00:03:50,800
Can you ask the owner

68
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,120
if he has any other sizes?

69
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,400
Alright.

70
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,590
I'll go now.

71
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,960
Be careful in there.

72
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:02,080
Can you stop making things
difficult for me?

73
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:37,900
♪Every time the waves rolled in♪

74
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:42,020
♪You stared endlessly at them♪

75
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:45,900
♪I missed the time
when the sun reflected the past♪

76
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:49,860
♪What is left to love?♪

77
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:53,020
♪I thought you were an angel♪

78
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:55,140
♪My guardian angel♪

79
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:58,100
♪You have seen all of me♪

80
00:04:58,460 --> 00:05:00,860
♪Until reality overflowed♪

81
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:03,020
♪With your sensibility♪

82
00:05:03,540 --> 00:05:07,540
♪You finally escaped reality♪

83
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:10,500
♪I could hear all the people♪

84
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:12,700
♪Cheered for you♪

85
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:14,580
♪I hid in the cape after the rain♪

86
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:16,860
♪So I couldn't hear your turmoil♪

87
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:20,700
♪I spread my arms for one last embrace♪

88
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:23,860
♪But you escaped between the gaps♪

89
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:26,300
♪I could hear all the people♪

90
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:28,540
♪Cheered for you♪

91
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:30,750
Wenyu.

92
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:32,860
♪So I couldn't hear your turmoil♪

93
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:36,620
♪I spread my arms for one last embrace♪

94
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:39,900
♪But you escaped between the gaps♪

95
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:42,500
♪I watched the seasons change♪

96
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:44,540
♪I thought we will have time♪

97
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:46,540
♪But I couldn't endure the storms♪

98
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:48,820
♪You made my heart panic♪

99
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:52,820
♪No matter how absurd,
I learned to value♪

100
00:05:53,340 --> 00:05:57,340
♪My own worth♪

101
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:04,160
I'm full.

102
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:13,900
♪I could hear all the people♪

103
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:16,020
♪Cheered for you♪

104
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:17,720
Have a bit more.

105
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:19,630
I'm leaving now.

106
