♪I spread my arms for one last embrace♪

107
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:27,300
♪But you escaped between the gaps♪

108
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:29,940
♪I watched the seasons change♪

109
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:31,980
♪I thought we will have time♪

110
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,940
♪But I couldn't endure the storms♪

111
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:36,300
♪You made my heart panic♪

112
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:40,300
♪No matter how absurd,
I learned to value♪

113
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:44,740
♪My own worth♪

114
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:00,920
Miss, you called for me?

115
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,000
Bitao,

116
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:04,720
go to the best matchmaker in Feng City.

117
00:07:05,149 --> 00:07:06,630
Ask her to find a lady
from every noble family

118
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:08,310
around the Major General's age.

119
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,800
Remember,

120
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,360
she must pick the best one.

121
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,480
Miss,

122
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:14,360
you are...

123
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,510
I plan on finding
a good marriage for Xunchu

124
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:19,000
and help him start a family.

125
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:21,360
It will appease the Commander's spirit.

126
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,310
- Yes, Miss.
- Go on.

127
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,510
Who allowed you to come in?

128
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:53,630
Get out.

129
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:03,240
Did you ask Bitao to find me a matchmaker?

130
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,360
Yes.

131
00:08:05,658 --> 00:08:07,360
I told her to look out
for young women of the right age.

132
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,750
Who told you to meddle in my business?

133
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,680
A sister-in-law is as good as a mother.
I am not meddling.

134
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,830
Let go.

135
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,480
You... You.

136
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:20,240
Lin Wenyu,

137
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,240
have you ever asked me

138
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,390
what type of woman I like?

139
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,040
You're drunk, Duan Xunchu.

140
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,870
Get out of my room.

141
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,870
Ask me.

142
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,320
What type do you like?

143
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,790
What if I tell you

144
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,750
that you're the type I like,

145
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,200
that you're the one like?

146
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,080
Stop your nonsense.

147
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,360
I'm your sister-in-law.

148
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,200
Sister-in-law?

149
00:08:57,510 --> 00:09:00,120
You and my brother's betrothal is only
a verbal arrangement by the parents.

150
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,790
You aren't even properly engaged.

151
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:05,360
You aren't my sister-in-law.

152
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:08,240
Let go.

153
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:09,910
Sober up.

154
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,270
Duan Xunchu,

155
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,390
don't you have the slightest sense

156
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:14,200
of propriety?

157
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:21,960
Propriety?

158
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,790
If I knew what propriety is,

159
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:27,870
I wouldn't have fallen in love
with my own sister-in-law.

160
00:09:56,360 --> 00:10:00,920
♪Looking deep into her heart♪

161
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:06,640
♪Looking at each other
under the moonlight in secret♪

162
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:12,880
♪This reunion came unexpectedly♪

163
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:18,720
♪Your face is unforgettable♪

164
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:22,000
♪In the time that passed us by♪

165
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,880
♪My love turned into a lie♪

166
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:30,880
♪I bury thousands of words
behind an icy facade♪

167
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:33,760
♪Our shadows locked in an embrace♪

168
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,840
♪Finally find a home♪

169
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:42,840
♪Never fear the eternity♪
